A '''ring''' is an [[equipment]] item in ''[[RuneScape]]'' worn in the ring slot of the [[Worn equipment|equipped inventory menu]].

==Crafting rings==
These rings can be created with a ring mould, a gold bar and gems (optional) using the [[Crafting]] skill with the required Crafting level.

Rings are only decorative in [[free-to-play]], but in [[pay-to-play]] they may be [[enchant]]ed to gain special bonuses. Enchanting a ring (must contain a [[gem]]) requires the [[runes]] and [[Magic]] level necessary to cast the appropriate enchantment [[spell]].

